@node Introduction "Introduction to MCEd"

  @{b}@{u}Introduction@{uu}@{ub}

      This package contains 8 ARexx scripts for use with @{i}CygnusEd
  Professional@{ui} 3.5 or higher. They provide basic wordprocessing capabilities
  and may also be useful to programmers. Here is a list of included scripts:

  @{"   Indent.ced  " link Indent} - indents line/block;
  @{"MakeComment.ced" link MakeComment} - makes boxed comments;
  @{" MultiView.ced " link MultiView} - shows current file according to it's type;
  @{"  Outdent.ced  " link Outdent} - outdents line/block;
  @{"  Paginate.ced " link Paginate} - adds page numbers to text;
  @{"  Preview.ced  " link Preview} - shows text with formatting;
  @{"   Stats.ced   " link Stats} - displays basic statistics for text;
  @{"   Undo.ced    " link Undo} - undoes effects of any MCEd's script;

@endnode

@node Requirements "Requirements for MCEd"

  @{b}@{u}Requirements@{uu}@{ub}

      All scripts require ARexx and @{i}CygnusEd Professional@{ui} version 3.5 (or
  higher).
      @{"  Preview.ced  " link Preview} requires @{i}MultiView@{ui} (AmigaDOS 3.0 or higher).
@endnode

@node Installation "Installation of MCEd"

  @{b}@{u}Installation@{uu}@{ub}

      Use supplied @{i}Installer@{ui} script to copy files. Then, in @{i}CygnusEd@{ui}, choose
  @{i}"ARexx interface/Install ARexx command..."@{ui} menu option to enter paths,
  names and parameters for the scripts. Don't forget to run @{i}RexxMast@{ui} before
  using any of these scripts!
@endnode

@node History "MCEd History"

  @{b}@{u}History@{uu}@{ub}

      Version 1.0 (2.1.95) - initial release

      Version 1.1 (10.2.95):

    Improvements:
    · @{"MakeComment.ced" link MakeComment} can now just comment-out a line;
    · @{"   Indent.ced  " link Indent} script added;
    · @{"  Outdent.ced  " link Outdent} script added.

    Bug fixes:
    · @{"  Preview.ced  " link Preview} could not start @{i}MultiView@{ui} if one had been using
      @{i}topaz.font 8@{ui} or @{i}topaz.font 9@{ui}.

      Version 1.2 (30.3.95):

    Improvements:
    · @{" MultiView.ced " link MultiView} script added.
@endnode

